<h1>I-9 Section 1 Complete</h1>

<p>Hello,</p>

<p>
  <strong><%= @candidate.full_name %></strong> has completed Section 1 of their I-9 form
  for the <strong><%= @job.title %></strong> position.
</p>

<h2>Action Required</h2>

<p>
  You must complete Section 2 of the I-9 form by <strong><%= @deadline&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></strong>
  (within 3 business days of the employee's start date).
</p>

<p>
  Section 2 requires you to:
</p>

<ul>
  <li>Physically examine the employee's original identity and employment authorization documents</li>
  <li>Record the document information in Section 2</li>
  <li>Sign and date the form</li>
</ul>

<h2>Employee Details</h2>

<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Employee:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @candidate.full_name %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Position:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @job.title %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Start Date:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @i9_verification&.employee_start_date&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>Section 2 Deadline:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><%= @deadline&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
  <strong>Important:</strong> Completing Section 2 on time is a federal requirement.
  Late completion may result in penalties.
</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br>
  <%= PlatformBrand.name %> System
</p>
